The  following symbols have been used beside the original symbols at either of the below URLs:
http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/List_of_symbols
http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Bengali_and_English/TagSets

ppd= d participle
ppe= e participle
opt= optaitive verb 

The speling format details are availabe at http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Speling_format.
The classification of the words used in the nepali speling format is based on the NeLRaLec Tageset. 
The original NeLRaLec Tageset is available at http://www.bhashasanchar.org/pdfs/nelralec-wp-tagset.pdf

The words used in building the speling lists were taken from the Nepali National Coprus(http://www.bhashasanchar.org/ncorpus_written.php).

